        5 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0662P0-03545'>
        <a name='S5LV0662P0_20040615_GCR_97'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-sainsbury' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0662P0_20040615_GCR_97' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Sainsbury' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
